'''Aḥmad Badduj''' (1950 - 22 Ɣuct 2020) iga yan zɣ inmɣuṛn n taẓuṛi taclḥit tamaziɣt, ilul ɣ useggas n 1950 ɣ Msgina igan yan udwar n Ifrxs itabɛan i [[Agadir|Ugadir]], tasga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus Massa]]. Dars uggar n 30 film s tutlayt [[taclḥit]].

== Tudrt-nns ==
Aḥmad Badduj iga yuws n Talburjt ɣ [[Agadir|Ugadir]]. Iswurri ɣ kigan n twuriwin lli ɣ d yumẓ lbac nns, ilɛb akk d iɛrrimn n [[Talḥasant n Ugadir|Talḥasant n ugadir]] ɣ usggwas n 1967.

Ɣ usggwas n 1972 ifta s [[Inzggan]], ɣin aɣ iskr trabbut nns tamzwarut n lmṣraḥ s [[Taclḥit|tmaziɣt]] iga yas s yism "''Amnar Umrr''". Izri nn ɣ tuggt n trubba yaḍni aylliɣ ikcm d tamsmunt n Tifawin ɣ isggwas n 1985, zɣ lliɣ disn ikcm as ibda ar ittuyssan ɣ ammas n ubaraz n tẓuri d lmaṣraḥ amaziɣ.

Ɣ usggwas n 1989 icark ɣ ṭṭṣwir n lfilm lli akk izwarn s tutlayt [[taclḥit]] d akk [[tutlayin timaziɣin]] at igan "[[Tamɣart n Wurɣ|''Tamɣart n wurɣ'']]". Zɣ ɣ-akud-ann icark ɣ kigan n laflam yaḍni iskr akk ntta talif d lixraj.

Immut igllin n Aḥmad Badduj s tmaḍunt n [[Aṭṭan n kurunafirus 2019|Kurunafirus]] ɣ wass n 20 ɣuct 2020 ɣ [[Agadir|Ugadir]]. Ikka-tt-inn yad ihrc s sskar d wul

